---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Enterprise Growth Partnerships | High-Scale Edinburgh Marketing" description="Revenue-shared and performance-based marketing partnerships for established Edinburgh firms looking for board-level strategy.">
	<section class="py-32 bg-[#0A192F] relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
			<div class="absolute top-0 -left-4 w-96 h-96 bg-[#6B4C9A] rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-[150px] opacity-20 animate-pulse"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
			<span class="text-xs font-black text-[#6B4C9A] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-8 block">Exclusive Partnership Tier</span>
			<h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-8">
				Performance-Led <br/><span class="text-[#6B4C9A]">Market Dominance.</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-purple-100/60 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
				We don't just bill for hours. For established Edinburgh firms, we offer revenue-linked partnerships where we take a stake in the growth we generate.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-6">
				<a href="/contact" class="bg-[#6B4C9A] text-white px-12 py-6 rounded-2xl font-black text-xl hover:bg-[#5A3B8A] transition-all shadow-2xl">
					Request Private Briefing
				</a>
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-4 text-white/40 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">
					<span>Min. £1M Annual Revenue Required</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-32 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-24 items-center">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-sm font-black text-[#6B4C9A] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6">Skin in the Game</h2>
					<h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-[#0A192F] leading-tight mb-8">
						Why Performance <br/>Partnerships?
					</h3>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-500 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
						Standard agency models are broken. They get paid regardless of your growth. Our Enterprise model flips this on its head. We align our incentives directly with your bottom line.
					</p>
					
					<div class="space-y-8">
						<div class="flex items-start p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 group hover:border-[#6B4C9A]/30 transition-all">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#0A192F] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0 text-white font-bold">01</div>
							<div>
								<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0A192F] mb-2">Revenue Operations (RevOps)</h4>
								<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">We optimize your entire sales and marketing funnel to ensure maximum efficiency at every stage.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 group hover:border-[#6B4C9A]/30 transition-all">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#0A192F] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0 text-white font-bold">02</div>
							<div>
								<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0A192F] mb-2">Omni-Channel Saturation</h4>
								<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">We dominate every digital touchpoint where your high-value Edinburgh clients live and work.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 group hover:border-[#6B4C9A]/30 transition-all">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#0A192F] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0 text-white font-bold">03</div>
							<div>
								<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0A192F] mb-2">Board-Level Reporting</h4>
								<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Direct communication with your executive team on high-level growth metrics and market positioning.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1A2E4C] to-[#0A192F] p-12 lg:p-20 rounded-[4rem] text-white relative overflow-hidden">
					<div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-60 h-60 bg-[#6B4C9A] rounded-full filter blur-[100px] opacity-30"></div>
					<h4 class="text-3xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight">The "No-Risk" <br/>Enterprise Offer</h4>
					<p class="text-purple-100/60 mb-12 text-lg leading-relaxed">We provide a full strategic audit and implementation roadmap. If we don't hit agreed-upon growth milestones, you don't pay our performance bonuses.</p>
					
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
						<div class="p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10">
							<span class="text-3xl font-black block mb-1">£5M+</span>
							<span class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Revenue Managed</span>
						</div>
						<div class="p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10">
							<span class="text-3xl font-black block mb-1">100%</span>
							<span class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Goal Alignment</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<a href="/contact" class="block w-full bg-white text-[#0A192F] py-5 rounded-2xl font-black text-center hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all shadow-xl">
						Request Executive Briefing
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Growth Engine Section -->
	<section class="py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center mb-24">
				<h2 class="text-sm font-black text-[#6B4C9A] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-4">Engineered for Scale</h2>
				<p class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-[#0A192F]">The 24/7 Growth <span class="text-[#6B4C9A]">Machine.</span></p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[3rem] border border-gray-100 group hover:bg-[#0A192F] transition-all duration-500">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#6B4C9A]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#6B4C9A] group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h4 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#0A192F] group-hover:text-white mb-4 transition-colors">AI-First Optimization</h4>
					<p class="text-gray-500 group-hover:text-purple-100/60 leading-relaxed transition-colors">
						Our custom-built AI agents monitor your ad spend and keyword rankings every 60 seconds, making micro-adjustments that human teams miss.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[3rem] border border-gray-100 group hover:bg-[#0A192F] transition-all duration-500">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#6B4C9A]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#6B4C9A] group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9-9c1.657 0 3 4.03 3 9s-1.343 9-3 9m0-18c-1.657 0-3 4.03-3 9s1.343 9 3 9m-9-9a9 9 0 019-9"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h4 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#0A192F] group-hover:text-white mb-4 transition-colors">Global Specialist Hub</h4>
					<p class="text-gray-500 group-hover:text-purple-100/60 leading-relaxed transition-colors">
						Your account is managed by senior strategists in Edinburgh, but delivered by our elite technical hub in the Philippines, ensuring 24/7 campaign velocity.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[3rem] border border-gray-100 group hover:bg-[#0A192F] transition-all duration-500">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#6B4C9A]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#6B4C9A] group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-7.618 3.04C5.459 9.131 5.821 11.512 7.062 13.523a9.981 9.981 0 001.295 1.545 11.93 11.93 0 012.308-1.442c.707-.348 1.487-.525 2.275-.525.787 0 1.567.177 2.275.525a11.921 11.921 0 012.308 1.442 9.98 9.98 0 001.295-1.545c1.241-2.011 1.603-4.392 2.256-7.539z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h4 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#0A192F] group-hover:text-white mb-4 transition-colors">SOP-Driven Quality</h4>
					<p class="text-gray-500 group-hover:text-purple-100/60 leading-relaxed transition-colors">
						Every task is governed by 15 years of refined Standard Operating Procedures. We don't rely on "luck"—we rely on a proven growth engine.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	</section>

	<!-- Comparison Table Section -->
	<section class="py-32 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center mb-24">
				<h2 class="text-sm font-black text-[#6B4C9A] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-4">Choose Your Velocity</h2>
				<p class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-[#0A192F]">Partnership <span class="text-[#6B4C9A]">Tiers.</span></p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
				<!-- Tier 1: Blueprint -->
				<div class="p-12 rounded-[3.5rem] border border-gray-100 bg-slate-50 relative group">
					<div class="mb-10">
						<span class="text-xs font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest block mb-4">Immediate Start</span>
						<h4 class="text-3xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-2">Revenue Blueprint</h4>
						<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm italic">Our most popular entry-level strategic product.</p>
					</div>
					<ul class="space-y-6 mb-12">
						<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							Full Technical SEO Audit
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							12-Month Content Roadmap
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							PPC Efficiency Deep-Dive
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600 opacity-50">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg>
							Revenue-Share Alignment
						</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="text-2xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-8">£1,950 <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest ml-2">Secure Online Payment</span></div>
					<a href="/contact" class="block w-full py-5 rounded-2xl bg-[#0A192F] text-white text-center font-black hover:bg-[#1A2E4C] transition-all shadow-xl">Buy Now & Start Audit</a>
					<p class="text-[10px] text-center text-gray-400 mt-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Delivered by our Strategy Team in 10 Days</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Tier 2: Machine -->
				<div class="p-12 rounded-[3.5rem] bg-[#0A192F] text-white shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group transform scale-105 border-4 border-[#6B4C9A]">
					<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8">
						<span class="bg-[#6B4C9A] text-white px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest animate-pulse">Highest Value</span>
					</div>
					<div class="mb-10">
						<span class="text-xs font-black text-[#6B4C9A] uppercase tracking-widest block mb-4">Strategic Tier</span>
						<h4 class="text-3xl font-black mb-2">Growth Engine</h4>
						<p class="text-purple-100/40 text-sm italic">The multi-channel partner.</p>
					</div>
					<ul class="space-y-6 mb-12">
						<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-purple-100">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#6B4C9A] mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							Elite Strategic Audit Included
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-purple-100">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#6B4C9A] mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							Full Technical Execution (SEO+PPC)
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-purple-100">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#6B4C9A] mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							24/7 AI-Powered Optimization
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-purple-100">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#6B4C9A] mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							Revenue-Share Milestones
						</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="text-2xl font-black mb-8">From £4,500 <span class="text-xs text-[#6B4C9A] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest ml-2">+ Performance</span></div>
					<a href="/contact" class="block w-full py-5 rounded-2xl bg-[#6B4C9A] text-white text-center font-black hover:bg-[#5A3B8A] transition-all shadow-xl shadow-purple-900/40">Request Private Briefing</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Criteria Section -->
	<section class="py-32 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-24 items-center">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-sm font-black text-[#6B4C9A] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-6">Who We Work With</h2>
					<h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-[#0A192F] leading-tight mb-8">
						Not Everyone is a <br/><span class="text-[#6B4C9A]">Fit.</span>
					</h3>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-500 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
						To maintain our 98% retention rate and 24/7 delivery quality, we are intentionally selective. We only partner with Edinburgh firms where we know we can deliver a minimum 5x-10x ROI.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between group">
						<span class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0A192F]">Established Revenue (£1M+)</span>
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between group">
						<span class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0A192F]">Dedicated Internal Sales Team</span>
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between group">
						<span class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0A192F]">Long-Term Growth Mindset</span>
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<p class="text-xs font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest text-center pt-4">
						We currently have 1 partnership opening for Q2 2026.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Roadmap Section -->
	<section class="py-32 bg-[#0A192F] relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center mb-24">
				<h2 class="text-sm font-black text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-4">The Partnership Journey</h2>
				<p class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white">Your 12-Month <span class="text-[#6B4C9A]">Roadmap.</span></p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
				<div class="p-10 bg-white/5 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 relative group hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
					<span class="text-xs font-black text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 block">Months 1-2</span>
					<h4 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Infrastructure & Audit</h4>
					<p class="text-purple-100/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Full technical overhaul, funnel leak patching, and baseline data calibration.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-10 bg-white/5 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 relative group hover:bg-white/10 transition-all lg:mt-12">
					<span class="text-xs font-black text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 block">Months 3-5</span>
					<h4 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Aggressive Acquisition</h4>
					<p class="text-purple-100/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Launch of high-intent PPC and Local SEO "Land Grab" across Edinburgh EH postcodes.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-10 bg-white/5 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 relative group hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
					<span class="text-xs font-black text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 block">Months 6-9</span>
					<h4 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Scale & Optimization</h4>
					<p class="text-purple-100/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Double down on winning channels and launch automated multi-channel retargeting.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-10 bg-white/5 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 relative group hover:bg-white/10 transition-all lg:mt-12">
					<span class="text-xs font-black text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 block">Months 10-12+</span>
					<h4 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Market Dominance</h4>
					<p class="text-purple-100/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Consolidating EH market share and expanding into national Scottish growth tiers.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Productized Audit Section -->
	<section class="py-32 bg-slate-50 border-t border-gray-100">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="bg-white rounded-[4rem] p-12 lg:p-24 shadow-2xl border border-gray-100 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">
				<div class="flex-1">
					<span class="text-xs font-black text-[#6B4C9A] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-6 block">The First Step</span>
					<h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-8 leading-tight">The 7-Figure <br/><span class="text-[#6B4C9A]">Revenue Blueprint.</span></h3>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-500 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
						Not ready for a full partnership? Our Revenue Blueprint is a deep-dive, board-ready strategic audit that identifies exactly where your revenue leaks are and how to fix them.
					</p>
					<ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
						<li class="flex items-center text-[#0A192F] font-bold text-sm">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							Full Funnel Leak Analysis
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center text-[#0A192F] font-bold text-sm">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							Competitor Spend Intelligence
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center text-[#0A192F] font-bold text-sm">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							Technical Growth Roadmap
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center text-[#0A192F] font-bold text-sm">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
							Board-Level Presentation
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="w-full lg:w-96 bg-slate-50 p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-gray-100 text-center">
					<span class="text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-4 block">Fixed Price Investment</span>
